# Dental-Clinic-Management-System-
A BCA level project to manage dental clinic operations like patient records and billings
# Dental Clinic Management System

This is a conceptual project developed during my BCA program. It is designed to assist dental clinics in managing daily operations efficiently.

## Key Features:
- Patient registration and medical records
- Appointment scheduling
- Treatment tracking
- Billing and payment management

## Project Type:
- Academic (Synopsis-based)
- No code implementation; focuses on project planning and system design

## Documentation:
The attached synopsis outlines the entire system workflow, features, and data flow diagrams.

